<br>
Requirements:<br>
Lvl 62+ or keyed or flagged for CoD, Tactics, HoH, Storms, and BoT.<br>
Resist gear enabling you to be close to 100 on all resists.<br>
NO WHINERS. When I lead a raid I dont like to be told what to do and I dont like the company of people that have a 65 this and a 65 that on another server and have killed mob VII 80 times. I am totally open to suggestions though and gladly take input.<br>
<br>
These raids are mainly for people that are in a non raiding guild, love their guild, but still want to raid and have a chance at some nicer items that they normally wouldnt. I havent decided if I will make it neut/evil only yet since I have no idea how many will show, if any at all.<br>
<br>
Loot:<br>
Always a big question. Ill make it easy. NBG and random will be used. If this becomes something popular then I will give modifiers to people that frequent the raids and contribute more time to them.<br>
<br>
Targets:<br>
From Vindi to Kunark Dragons to BoT tower bosses. Whatever we have the force to do and whatever everyone wants to try (what is up of course) will be targetted. All will depend on turn out.<br>
<br>
If you have any questions I will try and answer them here. No need for sign ups, just /join openraid on saturday mornings and we will go from there.<br>
<br>
FYI, I tolerate NO punks and asshats, so if you are being one expect to see a TL message pop up on your screen and a raid boot. I enjoy fun and challenges. Jokes are always welcome too.<br>
<br>
Diablita Di'Asmodea<br>
